Class BmpCharMatcher

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Cloneable, Matcher, Rule, GraphNode<Matcher>

    public class BmpCharMatcher
extends UnicodeCharMatcher
    A UnicodeCharMatcher for characters inside the basic multilingual plane

    The basic multilingual plane includes all code points in the range U+0000 to U+FFFF, as far as Java is concerned, there is a one-to-one match between such a code point and a char, so what this does is simply delegate the job to a CharMatcher.
